ZH: 我悔悟了自己的错误。
EN: I have realized my mistakes.

ZH: 他悔悟了不好好读书的后果。
EN: He regretted not studying properly and realizing its consequences.

ZH: 她悔悟了对朋友的冷漠。
EN: She regretted being indifferent to her friends.

